tariffs-2024-05-16/</link><description>行业高管和分析师表示，印度钢铁行业已经因进口廉价商品而陷入困境，在美国对中国钢铁征收关税后，印度钢铁行业担心来自中国的出货量激增。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 08:02:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-steel-mills-fear-surge-chinese-imports-after-us-tariffs-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾组织称南海民事任务是“重大胜利”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-group-calls-civilian-mission-south-china-sea-major-victory-2024-05-16/</link><description>菲律宾一个在南海执行民用补给任务的菲律宾组织官员周四表示，尽管遭到中国船只的跟踪，但仍向菲律宾渔民运送了食品和燃料，并称这是一次“重大胜利”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 07:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-group-calls-civilian-mission-south-china-sea-major-victory-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫称瑞士乌克兰问题会议毫无意义</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-switzerland-conference-ukraine-is-futile-2024-05-16/</link><description>克里姆林宫表示，瑞士希望为乌克兰和平进程铺平道路的计划中的峰会如果没有俄罗斯的参与将是徒劳的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 05:49:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-switzerland-conference-ukraine-is-futile-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡航空首席执行官表示，中国出境旅行尚未恢复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/singapore-airlines-ceo-says-travel-out-china-not-yet-recovered-2024-05-16/</link><description>新加坡航空公司首席执行官周四表示，来自中国的航空旅行需求尚未恢复到新冠疫情大流行前的水平，但中国公民前往亚洲枢纽的免签证计划有助于填补座位，该航空公司今年将增加更多中国运力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 05:34:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/singapore-airlines-ceo-says-travel-out-china-not-yet-recovered-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国提高对中国的关税，依赖中国的越南的进口猛增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-hikes-china-tariffs-imports-soar-china-reliant-vietnam-2024-05-16/</link><description>数据显示，随着美国加大力度通过提高关税来减少对华贸易，极大地增加了从越南的进口，而越南的大部分出口依赖中国的投入。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 05:15:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-hikes-china-tariffs-imports-soar-china-reliant-vietnam-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>Temu成为欧盟消费者组织向欧盟科技监管机构投诉的目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-targeted-eu-consumer-groups-complaint-eu-tech-regulator-2024-05-16/</link><description>中国快时尚电子商务零售商特木周四因拼多多集团旗下业务可能违反在线内容规则而遭到欧盟投诉。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 04:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-targeted-eu-consumer-groups-complaint-eu-tech-regulator-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>中美关系紧张，微软要求部分中国员工搬迁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-asks-hundreds-china-based-staff-relocate-amid-us-china-tensions-wsj-2024-05-16/</link><description>该公司周四表示，随着中美关系因人工智能和半导体等技术而变得日益紧张，微软正在要求部分中国员工考虑调往国外。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 04:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-asks-hundreds-china-based-staff-relocate-amid-us-china-tensions-wsj-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>台湾即将上任的总统面临愤怒的中国和分裂的议会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-incoming-president-faces-angry-china-fractured-parliament-2024-05-16/</link><description>赖清德周一就任台湾总统，面临着中国称他为“危险的分裂分子”并加强了军事演习，以及国内议会四分五裂、没有任何政党占多数的局面。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 03:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-incoming-president-faces-angry-china-fractured-parliament-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产股因政府计划购买未售出房屋而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-shares-hk-jump-report-government-plans-buy-unsold-homes-2024-05-16/</link><description>有报道称，中国正在考虑一项计划，让全国各地的地方政府从陷入困境的公司购买数百万套未售出的房屋，以缓解旷日持久的房地产危机，中国房地产开发商的股价周四上涨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 02:22:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-shares-hk-jump-report-government-plans-buy-unsold-homes-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国蔚来汽车计划每年推出一款Onvo品牌新车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-aims-launch-one-new-car-model-per-year-under-onvo-brand-2024-05-16/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车周四表示，该公司将在中国过度拥挤的汽车市场上将其产品阵容扩大到家庭用车，每年将推出一款价格较低的 Onvo 品牌的新车型，并将其定价与汽油车类似。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 02:10:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-aims-launch-one-new-car-model-per-year-under-onvo-brand-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市跟随华尔街上涨，美元因通胀缓解而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-16/</link><description>亚洲股市周四上涨，因美国通胀报告温和，提高了美联储今年将实施两次降息的预期，隔夜华尔街股市飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 02:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>美国通胀回落后，日元上涨，美元企稳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-sags-slower-us-inflation-boosts-rate-cut-expectations-2024-05-16/</link><description>周三数据显示美国通胀放缓后，日元周四连续第二天上涨，而美元兑其他货币在前一天大幅下跌后站稳脚跟。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 00:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-sags-slower-us-inflation-boosts-rate-cut-expectations-2024-05-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>